latestIgtvVideos.title: We are ONE and we are INDIA UNITED.
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Taking small chances of this lockdown, I'm learning to edit videos. And finally, I could come up with this, which is not the best. I know I've so much to learn and I hope this video will keep your stress and fears away for a while.

These footage are from my recent tour of the Northeast under the banner "Breaking Stereotype and Redefining Northeast."

PS: Our Northeast is as beautiful as it can get and to all the citizens of this beautiful nation, I would urge you all to stop the dreaded racial discrimination. We are ONE and we are India United!

With love and prayers❤️

Music by: The Konflated poets - Welcome to the Northeast.
